org.sql: SELECT custom_values.value FROM custom_values LEFT OUTER JOIN custom_fields ON custom_fields.id = custom_values.custom_field_id WHERE custom_values.customized_id = "$1" AND custom_values.customized_type = "$2" AND custom_values.custom_field_id = "$3" ORDER BY custom_fields.position
